question: Determine the year the television series Friends first aired, then using only historical records of corporate founding dates from that year prior to October, identify the pioneering e-commerce entity originally established as an online bookstore that became a transformative digital retail platform.
subject: web_search
derived_ev: The TV show Friends first aired in 1994
Amazon.com was founded by Jeff Bezos in July 1994 as an online bookstore and later became a pioneering e-commerce giant that transformed digital retail
The historically significant technology company founded in the same year Friends first aired is Amazon

tier1_result.reasoning: Answers agree because the solver's "Amazon" matches the expected "Amazon". Amazon was founded July 5, 1994—before Friends premiered on September 22, 1994—and it began as an online bookstore that became a transformative digital retail platform, meeting all criteria.
